# NPSSO tokens for PSN authentication — one per player who signs in directly.
# Get yours: log in at https://www.playstation.com, then visit
# https://ca.account.sony.com/api/v1/ssocookie and copy the "npsso" value.
# Tokens expire (~2 months); re-grab when sync starts failing with auth errors.
#
# NEVER commit a real .env file. Copy this to .env and fill in values.
NPSSO_DAD=
NPSSO_BRAIDAN=
